@chapter The Symmetry Library
@cindex symmetry
@cindex point group

The symmetry library implements a few basic ideas in group theory.  Namely
it provides a character table for a given point group.  Currently it does
not support the cubic point groups (eg Td or Ih).  The only classes
intended for public consumption are the @code{CharacterTable} and 
@code{PointGroup} classes.  @code{PointGroup} stores the Schoenflies symbol
for a point group, and can generate a @code{CharacterTable} on the fly.
A @code{CharacterTable} contains @code{IrreducibleRepresentation}s and
@code{SymmetryOperation}s.

The following include files are provided by the symmetry library:

